          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X16-700B-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X16-700B-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X16-700B-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-1" n="1">I'd hav\<hi rend="italics">?</hi>\ you to know, as sure as you're Dean</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-2" n="2">On Thursday my Cask of Obrien I'll drain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-3" n="3">If my wife is not willing, I say she's a quean</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-4" n="4">And my right to the Cellar I Gad I'll Maintain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-5" n="5">As bravely as any that fought at Dumblain.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-6" n="6">Go tell her it over &amp; over again</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-7" n="7">I hope as I ride to the town it wont rain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-8" n="8">For should it I fear it will cool my hot brain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-9" n="9">Intirely extinguish my poetic vein</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-10" n="10">And then I should be as stupid as Kain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-11" n="11">Who preach<hi rend="superscript">d</hi> on three Heads though he mention<hi rend="superscript">ḍ</hi> but twain.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-12" n="12">Now Wardel's in haste &amp; begins to Complain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-13" n="13">Your Most Humbles Servant Dear Sir I remain</l>
            <l rend="indent(5)" xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-14" n="14">||||T. S──n.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-15" n="15">Get Helsham Walmsley Delany &amp; some Grattans if there be any</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-16" n="16">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-700B-line-17" n="17">Take care you do not bid too many</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
